productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
I saw one of these in The Gambia and I bought one.
My neighbor Honora has one of these. She works as a reporter and she says it looks enormous.
I tried to nab it but got salad all over it.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
